import React from 'react';
import { FC } from "react";
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";



export const PartnerScreen : FC = () => {

return(

<Form>
        <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formHorizontalEmail">
          <Form.Label column sm={2}>
            Электронная почта
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm={10}>
            <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Email" plaintext readOnly defaultValue="example@kk.com"/>
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formHorizontalPhone">
          <Form.Label column sm={2}>
            Телефон
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm={10}>
            <Form.Control type="phone" placeholder="Phone" plaintext readOnly defaultValue="+79241234432"/>
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        </Form>

)


    
}
